# emf_nomad.1000
#
# Invoked on startup to build temples & tribes as necessary to preserve
# the culture+religion, as specified in province history, of each potentially
# nomad-affected province on the map at any playable start date. Each
# such province is given its own province_event, the ID of which is
# 1000 + <province ID> in this namespace.
#
# NOTE: None of these province events actually execute unless they are
# actually found to be empty/nomadic at runtime, so while there may be
# a lot of events here, very little of the code will actually be run for
# any given start.
#
# How these events were created: All event code following was generated
# automatically by a program which emulates CK2 history execution, written
# by secret ninjas. If in need, contact zijistark (azrinon@gmail.com) so that
# he may relay your message to said ninjas and deliver their reply.
character_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1000

# emf_nomad.1001 [1 - Vestisland]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1001
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norse religion = norse_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = norse
			religion = norse_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norwegian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = norwegian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.1004 [4 - Tyrone]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1004
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = irish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = irish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1255 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = irish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = irish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = irish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = irish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = saxon
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1101 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = english religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = english
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

			culture  = cumbric
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1101 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = english religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = english
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.1074 [74 - Guines]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1074
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = low_frankish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = low_frankish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1158 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = dutch religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = dutch
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norman religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = norman
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1101 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = frankish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = frankish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = swabian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = swabian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1171 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = german religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = german
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1156
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = galician religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = galician
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = andalusian_arabic
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = aragonese religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = aragonese
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

				limit = { culture = arpitan religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = arpitan
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1201 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = german religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = german
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes

			if = {

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}

			culture  = low_german
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes

				limit = { culture = lappish religion = finnish_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = lappish
			religion = finnish_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes

			if = {

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement

		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1100 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = southern_italian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = southern_italian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			}

			culture  = vepsian
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = russian
			religion = slavic_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = russian religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = russian
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = bohemian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			culture  = greek
			religion = orthodox

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = hungarian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = mari
			religion = finnish_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = russian religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}

			culture  = russian

			culture  = cuman

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = khorasani religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = khorasani
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = khorasani religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = khorasani
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement

			culture  = daylamite
			religion = shiite
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1685
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = kurdish religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = kurdish
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1201 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = kurdish religion = yazidi }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = kurdish
			religion = yazidi
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = levantine_arabic
			religion = miaphysite
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1099 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = armenian religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = armenian
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1171 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = levantine_arabic religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = levantine_arabic
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

				limit = { culture = turkish religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = turkish
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.1758 [758 - Seleukeia]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1758
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = greek religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = greek
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes

# emf_nomad.1785 [785 - Sinai]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1785
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = levantine_arabic religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = levantine_arabic
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	}

# emf_nomad.1812 [812 - Malta]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1812
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = greek religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = greek
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = sicilian_arabic religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = sicilian_arabic
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1148 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = sicilian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = sicilian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.1843 [843 - Marrakech]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1843
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = zanata religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = zanata
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = somali religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = somali
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = cuman religion = tengri_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = cuman
			religion = tengri_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1231 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = mongol religion = tengri_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = mongol
			religion = tengri_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.1926 [926 - Bambuk]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.1926
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = manden religion = west_african_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = manden
			religion = west_african_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	hide_window = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norse religion = norse_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = norse
			religion = norse_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = danish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = danish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1306 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = turkish religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = turkish
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = low_frankish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = low_frankish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1151 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = dutch religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = dutch
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}

# emf_nomad.2067 [1067 - Foerde]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.2067
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norse religion = norse_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = norse
			religion = norse_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norwegian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = norwegian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}


# emf_nomad.2068 [1068 - Toreida]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.2068
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = livonian
			religion = finnish_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1200 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = livonian religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = livonian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

# emf_nomad.2074 [1074 - Magdeburg]

	immediate = {

			culture  = pommeranian

			break = yes

		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }

				limit = { culture = low_saxon religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement

			culture  = low_saxon
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1101 } }

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = low_german
			religion = catholic

			break = yes
		}

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}

		}

			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = southern_italian
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = frankish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = castillan
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = tuareg religion = west_african_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = tuareg
			religion = west_african_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = tuareg religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}

			culture  = tuareg

province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.2255
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = occitan religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = occitan
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = russian
			religion = slavic_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = russian religion = orthodox }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = russian
			religion = orthodox
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = low_german
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = hausa religion = west_african_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = hausa
			religion = west_african_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			}

			culture  = baloch
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = soninke religion = west_african_pagan }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = soninke
			religion = west_african_pagan
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

				limit = { culture = tuareg religion = ibadi }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = tuareg
			religion = ibadi
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1111 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = tuareg religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = tuareg
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}

		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = norsegaelic religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = norsegaelic
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = cumbric religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = cumbric
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = scottish religion = catholic }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = scottish
			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			religion = catholic
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 1233 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = croatian religion = bogomilist }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = tribal }
			culture  = croatian
			religion = bogomilist
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = afghan
			religion = sunni

			limit = { not = { year = 1067 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = sindhi religion = sunni }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = sindhi
			religion = sunni
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}

			culture  = gujurati
			religion = jain
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}


# emf_nomad.2637 [1637 - Valabhi]
province_event = {
	id = emf_nomad.2637
	hide_window = yes
	is_triggered_only = yes

	trigger = { not = { any_province_holding = { not = { holding_type = nomad } } } }

	immediate = {
		if = {
			limit = { not = { year = 868 } }
			if = {
				limit = { culture = gujurati religion = jain }
				break = yes # Not necessary to build a settlement
			}
			build_holding = { type = temple }
			culture  = gujurati
			religion = jain
			emf_nomad_antinomad_effect = yes
			break = yes
		}
	}
}
